---
import SEMLayout from '../../layouts/SEMLayout.astro'
import SEMHero from '../../components/sem/SEMHero.astro'
import SEMCTASection from '../../components/sem/SEMCTASection.astro'
---

<SEMLayout
  title="Jack Storms — Optical Glass Sculptures — Case Study"
  description="Redefining luxury brand strategy for world-renowned glass art."
>
  <SEMHero
    title="Jack Storms — Optical Glass Sculptures"
    subtitle="Redefining luxury brand strategy for world-renowned glass art"
  />

  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-bold text-text-dark">Overview</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        Jack Storms is a world-famous optical glass sculptor whose work captivates collectors and art enthusiasts around the globe. Known for his intricate cold glass sculptures that refract light in mesmerizing ways, Jack needed a brand strategy that would match the prestige and craftsmanship of his art in the digital space.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Challenge -->
  <section class="bg-bg-light px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-bold text-text-dark">The Challenge</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        Positioning luxury art in a digital marketplace presents unique challenges. The tactile, light-refracting beauty of Jack's sculptures needed to translate into a compelling online experience. The brand had to convey exclusivity and craftsmanship while making the art accessible to a broader audience of potential collectors and enthusiasts worldwide.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-bold text-text-dark">Our Approach</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        Our team redefined the brand strategy with a sharp focus on luxury and exclusivity. We crafted a digital presence that mirrored the precision and artistry of Jack's work, developing content and messaging that told the story behind each sculpture. The strategy emphasized the rarity and craftsmanship of each piece, positioning Jack Storms not just as a sculptor but as a creator of heirloom-quality art objects.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results -->
  <section class="bg-bg-light px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-bold text-text-dark">Results</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white p-6 shadow-card text-center">
          <p class="font-accent text-h1 font-bold text-accent-blue">40%</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-body">Increase in Customer Engagement</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white p-6 shadow-card text-center">
          <p class="font-accent text-h1 font-bold text-accent-blue">Stronger</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-body">Market Presence Worldwide</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        The refined brand strategy resulted in a 40% increase in customer engagement and a significantly stronger market presence. The luxury positioning resonated with collectors and art enthusiasts, driving both awareness and sales in an increasingly competitive art market.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SEMCTASection
    title="Have a Similar Challenge?"
    description="Let's discuss how we can help your brand grow."
    ctaText="Start a Conversation"
    ctaHref="/contact"
  />
</SEMLayout>
